title: #265: Knife Hits in Alaska (@DanSoder)
itunes:title: Knife Hits in Alaska with Dan Soder
description: Dan Soder came over to my place to tell me all about the summer he spent working in a cannery in Alaska. The people he worked with were straight deigns without even realizing it. This might be the best summer job of all time.
